name: Pair_equalsTest
description: Unit tests for the equals method in the Pair class.

test_cases.name: testEquals_SameInstance
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with the same instance.

test_cases.name: testEquals_DifferentInstanceSameValues
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with different instances but same values.

test_cases.name: testEquals_DifferentInstanceDifferentValues
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with different instances and different values.

test_cases.name: testEquals_NotInstanceOfMapEntry
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with an object that is not an instance of Map.Entry.

test_cases.name: testEquals_InstanceOfMapEntryDifferentValues
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with an instance of Map.Entry but different values.

test_cases.name: testEquals_InstanceOfMapEntrySameValues
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with an instance of Map.Entry and same values.
